- Sorry.

57:04.514 --> 57:09.207
I think last night was my best shot
at catching this guy and I fucked it up.

57:10.407 --> 57:12.604
I don't know where
to go from here.

57:13.204 --> 57:15.901
If you can't go forwards,
go backwards.

57:16.201 --> 57:18.800
Back up. Who is he?
What do you know about him?

57:20.198 --> 57:22.295
He wants to kill?

57:22.395 --> 57:24.292
I mean, he's insane.

57:25.691 --> 57:28.089
I've spent years studying these guys.
They've all got their excuses.

57:28.289 --> 57:30.987
Fathers who beat them,
mothers who raped them...

57:31.187 --> 57:32.685
Voices tellin' them what to do...

57:32.885 --> 57:34.382
The bottom line is,
except for a very small percentage...

57:34.482 --> 57:36.482
